# Vocabulary App API Tests
# Use this file with the REST Client extension in VS Code

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5190/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

### Login with the user
POST http://localhost:5190/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

### Look up a word (no authentication required)
GET http://localhost:5190/api/words/search/hello

### Look up word definitions from external API
GET http://localhost:5190/api/words/definitions/hello

### Get user profile (requires authentication - replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN with actual token from login)
GET http://localhost:5190/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Update user profile (requires authentication - replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN with actual token from login)
PUT http://localhost:5190/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
    "email": "updated@example.com"
}